scene.message:
Nanjo: I will get to the root{nl}
of this without fail.{wait_fr:48} There{nl}
should be nothing I cannot do!{waitkey}{ret}

Patient: Nnngh, my bad tooth{nl}
is starting to ache.{waitkey}Do I really have to get all{nl}
the way over there just to{nl}
get it treated?!{waitkey}{ret}

Patient: Whatever comes, I'm{nl}
prepared for it, but I worry{nl}
about my little grandchild...{waitkey}They should be at school, so{nl}
I hope nothing's happened{nl}
there.{waitkey}{ret}
